{"tid":1707254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎明行動就係抗爭新模式, 俗D講句就係由朝打到晚!所以和理非一定要進化, 咁先真正做到和勇不分","createTime":"2019-11-11T09:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T14:13:47.000Z","uid":196536,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"44a359553ba4e06894c4fd4d8292267b42fc0eb4","tid":1707254,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:21:48.000Z","msg":"既然呢個殺人政權開始割班condom, 我地就一於送佢地一程!<br />\n抗爭無分晝夜, 要做到就要夠多人. Anytime, anywhere.<br />\n身份隱藏得夠好, 就有好多野可以做.<br />\n唔一定要你縱火, 條馬路咁大, 見到班狗咪唔好在行前退後直到見唔到為止, 每段塞你一分鐘你都死啦!<br />\n黨鐵戰線我諗今日有咁既成果都好多人被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求更安全玩法..<br />\n手足一定一定一定要小隊化切忌落單!<br />\n同埋<strong>小心藍屍廢老</strong>, 佢地有篤灰熱線, 見到直接神獸啦!<br />\n加油手足, 天佑香港! 無限期三罷未必而家就成功, 但突破樽頸都好緊要!<br />\n歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421e4c33ac1e638481338f9e6556c76874376585","tid":1707254,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:38:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81acd1b2eb8c1b986724ca925be7d792ec4a1f03","tid":1707254,"uid":110109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:44:10.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6944e28f2bbae310e5556f42072e333f69724c5c","tid":1707254,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81acd1b2eb8c1b986724ca925be7d792ec4a1f03","tid":1707254,"uid":110109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:44:10.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:01:36.000Z","msg":"手足好波!"},{"pid":"6cf3d3775d93ca517a493bc658461db76955fe57","tid":1707254,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81acd1b2eb8c1b986724ca925be7d792ec4a1f03","tid":1707254,"uid":110109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:44:10.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/no